# English Only

All project artifacts must be written in **English**:

- Documentation (`docs/`, `README.md`, guides)
- Cursor rules (`.cursor/rules/`)
- UI strings (labels, buttons, dialogs, log messages)
- Code comments and commit messages
- Shell script output and comments
- Error messages shown to the user

## Do not

- Add Portuguese, Spanish, or mixed-language docs
- Use Portuguese in `QMessageBox`, `QLabel`, or `appendLog()` strings
- Create `*-PT-BR.md` or locale-specific guides in the repo

## Exceptions

- External tool output (subfinder, nuclei, etc.) is shown as-is
- User-provided target URLs and scan data are not translated

## When editing

If you find non-English project text, translate it to English in the same change.
